For a set of {{2411.12449_FO0072||FO}} retrieved news chunks {{2411.12449_FO0073||FO}} sorted based on its time-stamp, batching gives {{2411.12449_FO0074||FO}}, where each batch contains {{2411.12449_FO0075||FO}} chunks. If {{2411.12449_FO0076||FO}} is not divisible by {{2411.12449_FO0077||FO}}, the last batch will contain <{{2411.12449_FO0078||FO}} chunks. This time-based sorting and batching approach allows information from similar dates---and thus similar events---to be grouped within the same prompt.